metadata.name: Midday heat
metadata.description:
The midday heat can be intense, but it also has its own unique charm and appeal. When the sun is high in the sky and the heat is at its peak, there is a sense of stillness and calm that can be both relaxing and invigorating.

Resolution: 3000x5100 px
Format: JPG (7.77 mb)
JKTLM, 2023
